snippet.title: Onimusha: Warlords - Gameplay Action Trailer
snippet.description:
What happens when a fierce samurai and nimble ninja confront throngs of demonic foes? Katanas slice and kunai fly in this action-packed trailer for Onimusha: Warlords - coming Jan 15th, 2019!
